      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><sub><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/graviton.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">&nbsp;</sub>Graviton Revelation</p>\n<p>You can cause your melee weapon to exert a gravitational pull, drawing strikes to meet it. If a creature hits you or a creature adjacent to you with a melee attack and you’re wielding a melee weapon, you can make a melee attack roll against the attacking creature as a reaction. If your attack exceeds the attacking creature’s KAC + 8, you don’t deal damage; instead, the target’s attack deals only half damage.</p>\n<div>\n<p>When you are attuned or fully attuned, you gain a +4 bonus to your attack roll to use this revelation.</p>\n</div>"
